咁都幾難識晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點先知自己算識夠"},{"pid":"0b1943cacebfd863bd168e3b339f0571ff5638e5","tid":543113,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8ed735a96c3c4a8a0fcd13cf0693a0322747f74","tid":543113,"uid":45773,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"哲學其實范圍都好大，有部分係唔需要科學底，有d就要識晒social science, normal science, psychology<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"哲學范圍好大。<br />\n有些需要文科底比較好（通常係social science, moral, 文化野，歷史野），有些需要理科底（如進化，生命起源，宇宙起源）比較好"},{"pid":"33d97a0cc465d89de0459f3d8b653b4dd9cbb551","tid":543113,"uid":145467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:32:23.000Z","msg":"不如樓主講下你覺得哲學係讀啲乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06955adeae6941109e645cc6b88d1b22e144d7be","tid":543113,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c701f2793dbd17a6ed17e9b05a089c56902f7ba","tid":543113,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"哲學一定關科學事架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"咁如果淨係討論science related嘅哲學命題，其實係咪要research先solve到? 「哲學」討論有咩價值?"},{"pid":"ad2c87d03e112efc4454704cb5b5bd74cf108f88","tid":543113,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:33:42.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係讀哲學 但有睇開哲學書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138f0a9cbecb09f13b5acaf1e55ba963a7f2f55d","tid":543113,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33d97a0cc465d89de0459f3d8b653b4dd9cbb551","tid":543113,"uid":145467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:32:23.000Z","msg":"不如樓主講下你覺得哲學係讀啲乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得哲學係不斷追問任何野嘅本質。 <br />\n<br />\n例如生命嘅本質係咩？日日番工食飯訓覺有咩意義？所以有存有主義，自由主義etc<br />\n例如人、動物點黎？所以有進化論，有神／無神論<br />\n再簡單d，上青樓如果你意我願，咁係咪ethical？<br />\n<br />\n但重點係哲學解決問題嘅方法係思辯 (可以想像姐係一班人係度吹水，發表己見) ，而唔係好似科學咁不斷用研究去prove right / wrong。"},{"pid":"4a17fb103162a57083af06e30e97a67e93e6d877","tid":543113,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:46:47.000Z","msg":"有無哲學JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dba642488f3d3d7ba9a9f4a1a14f2b4cd4e79d4","tid":543113,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:46:58.000Z","msg":"有無哲學JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad256222216b3865e293bb663510ec2f6d7f7a8","tid":543113,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"哲學系有文科生理科生 <br />\n<br />\n要唔要識科學<br />\n睇你讀咩範疇 同讀到咩程度 <br />\n一般入門嘅科學哲學，唔需要話好強嘅理科底都理解到 <br />\n但如果你講到做專業嘅科學哲學家，咁當然要受過科學訓練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02697a137d4ed0eae6cfa80e1c6feab6eee0079","tid":543113,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"去到最後會唔會大部分問題都得個講，無答案？"},{"pid":"2297c9d1405812fc57d13b780cc15e2484b15bdb","tid":543113,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"770a44233ab95ce5aabc5dbb0a5846db9d5da9fb","tid":543113,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8ed735a96c3c4a8a0fcd13cf0693a0322747f74","tid":543113,"uid":45773,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"哲學其實范圍都好大，有部分係唔需要科學底，有d就要識晒social science, normal science, psychology<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:29:11.000Z","msg":"咁都幾難識晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點先知自己算識夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點為之夠？好主觀架喎 <br />\n你做到專業哲學家都可以話唔夠嘅"},{"pid":"7113f34e74b2d611560f2b624fe7ebdb9caebf12","tid":543113,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dad256222216b3865e293bb663510ec2f6d7f7a8","tid":543113,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"哲學系有文科生理科生 <br />\n<br />\n要唔要識科學<br />\n睇你讀咩範疇 同讀到咩程度 <br />\n一般入門嘅科學哲學，唔需要話好強嘅理科底都理解到 <br />\n但如果你講到做專業嘅科學哲學家，咁當然要受過科學訓練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"有無人會讀完science degree再讀哲學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adc2ac7a8c54d5b64990cc1781cdcacc33bbdd6","tid":543113,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c02697a137d4ed0eae6cfa80e1c6feab6eee0079","tid":543113,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"去到最後會唔會大部分問題都得個講，無答案？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:52:47.000Z","msg":"冇標準答案 唔代表無答案 <br />\n好多哲學問題，哲學家都唔會搵到一個全部哲學家認同嘅睇法<br />\n但唔代表佢認為冇答案  <br />\n<br />\n要真係話一個哲學問題「無答案」 <br />\n唔可以話只係因為大家爭議不休，<br />\n而係要論證出，冇可能有客觀事實去解決問題"},{"pid":"cd548e48676481988ca5cfd23f8aad9e4b961e11","tid":543113,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7113f34e74b2d611560f2b624fe7ebdb9caebf12","tid":543113,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dad256222216b3865e293bb663510ec2f6d7f7a8","tid":543113,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"哲學系有文科生理科生 <br />\n<br />\n要唔要識科學<br />\n睇你讀咩範疇 同讀到咩程度 <br />\n一般入門嘅科學哲學，唔需要話好強嘅理科底都理解到 <br />\n但如果你講到做專業嘅科學哲學家，咁當然要受過科學訓練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"有無人會讀完science degree再讀哲學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy